Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.50,0:07:58.71,场面文本,Text,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs150\shad0\bord0\1c&H000000&\fnA1J6GI7I\pos(332.45,192.12)}|
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.71,0:07:58.96,场面文本,Text,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs150\shad0\bord0\1c&H000000&\fnA1J6GI7I\pos(332.45,192.12)}澤|
